data.meta_description: 94 likes, 2 comments - gigoity on June 19, 2024: "Austin Powers is a fictional character from the movie series “Austin Powers,” created by comedian Mike Myers. One of the funniest scenes in “Austin Powers: The Spy Who Shagged Me,” “How Did That Get In There?” The scene is a comedic moment where Austin, played by Mike Myers, and Felicity, played by Heather Graham, smuggle items hidden in suggestive ways during a physical exam.".
